===[[Idiom]]===
'''[[dressed]] [[to]] the [[nines]]'''
#{{idiom}} Very fancily or formally dressed; wearing very showy or splendid clothing.
#:''He arrived at the gala, '''dressed to the nines''' in his top hat and tails.''
